data.description: #5271-Charming Country Home situated on 1.7Ac+/- of Level Land. Boasting 3BD/2BTH & a Partially Open Floor Plan, this Property offers a Spacious & Comfortable Living Space. The Outdoor Features are Equally Impressive, including a Big Level Yard, a Shed for Storage, a Double Carport, & Mature Trees. Relax on the Front Porch or Entertain on the Generous Covered Back Patio. Additionally, Pickwick Lake provides Excellent Access to Water-Based Activities.
